: "126149631"}], "wikidata_url": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q94942192", "wikipedia_page_title": null, "added_wikidata_wikipedia_to_text_links": true, "_initial": "H", "url": "https://hls-dhs-dss.ch/it/articles/003655/2006-11-24"}